abstracts.cdata!:
The Fifth Sui Northern Project, which
            will support the Government's gas development plan
            designed to increase gas supplies in the country, consists
            of: (i) the expansion of the Sui Northern Gas Pipeline
            system to transmit and distribute an additional 70 MMCFD of
            gas which will be come available to SNGPL; and (ii)
            technical assistance to upgrade the management and
            operations of SNGPL.
